  int a = 5;
  int b = 10;
  int result = a + b;    // result = 15

â€¢ Concatenation is used with strings.
â€¢  It joins two or more strings together and Returns combined text.
  Example:
  string firstName = "Alok";
  string lastName = "Pandey";
  string fullName = firstName + " " + lastName;   // fullName = "Alok Pandey"

